dictionary.description: A bubbly, vivacious young lady with an unexpected fierceness when it comes to protecting her friends, Ochaco always tries to see the good in those around her. Her Quirk is Zero Gravity, which allows her to make any object she touches float in mid air. During the U.A.'s final exam, she eventually had to face her own feelings towards Izuku. Her quick thinking, however, saved the day and got her the win she needed to pass.
dictionary.summon: Everyone here is fighting for their futures! Does't that make us all rivals?
